snippet.title: ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS - Release Date Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch as King stuns his opponents! Play as Metal Knight, Stinger, Melzargard, and Dream Version Saitama!

Pre-Order today and be the hero who saves Earth when ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS releases on February 28, 2020: https://bandainam.co/OnePunchManPO

Coming to PS4, Xbox One, and PC.

#ONEPUNCHMAN #BandaiNamco
